title: RESILIENCY
itunes:title: RESILIENCY
itunes:subtitle: Motiversity
description:
RESILIENCY! If you give up now then they'll be right about you. You need to persist through the hardest times of your life. Be unstoppable, not without failures and doubt, but continue on in the face of everything.


New Motivational Speeches Compilation featuring some of the best motivational videos by Marcus A. Taylor (https://bit.ly/MarcusTaylorMotiversity) and Motiversity.


Music by Whitesand (https://www.youtube.com/c/WhitesandComposer), and Rok Nardin (https://www.youtube.com/c/RokNardin).


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
